lumes and reliefs, circles and squares, the collection honors the Maison’s penchant for geometry which dates back to the 1930s. Simultaneously it champions and eschews classic forms, balancing tradition with eccentricity.</p>\n\n[/testimonial]\n\n[/text_box]\n\n[/ux_banner]\n\n[/ux_slider]\n\n<!-- /wp:flatsome/uxbuilder -->', 'Trang chủ', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '60-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-08-27 09:13:38', '2021-08-27 16:13:38', '', 60, 'http://localhost:8888/banhang/?p=141', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
